===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{context|geometry}} A ([[convex]]) [[quadrilateral]] with two (non-adjacent) parallel sides.
# {{context|anatomy}} The [[trapezoid bone]] of the [[wrist]].
# {{context|geometry|British|obsolete}} A [[convex]] [[quadrilateral]] with no sides parallel and no equal sides.

